article.headline: Chavez powers Louisiana Tech to 68-55 victory over Nicholls
article.description: — Tahlik Chavez's 20 points helped Louisiana Tech defeat Nicholls 68-55 on Saturday.
article.linkText: Chavez powers Louisiana Tech to 68-55 victory over Nicholls
article.story: RUSTON, La. -- — Tahlik Chavez's 20 points helped Louisiana Tech defeat Nicholls 68-55 on Saturday. Chavez added seven rebounds for the Bulldogs (6-2). Devin Ree scored 15 points while going 6 of 8 (3 for 4 from 3-point range), and added six rebounds. Daniel Batcho shot 5 of 9 from the field and 4 for 4 from the line to finish with 14 points. The Colonels (3-6) were led by Jalen White, who recorded 16 points. Oumar Koureissi added 10 points and four blocks. In addition, Robert Brown III had eight points and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
